snippet.title: Breaking : Johnny Depp VS Amber Heard Case Delayed till 2021
snippet.description:
In this video we are going to talk about the new updates and recent court document of one of the most dramatic public divorces of recent times. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
_____________________________________________

There is no middle ground in the ongoing warfare between Johnny Depp and his ex-wife Amber Heard – and no end to the continuing toxicity of their relationship and divorce, now more than three years in the past. As quickly as Heard and  Depp burned bright, they just as speedily split up. Although their marriage lasted just 15 months, the battle in courts and in the court of public opinion continued. However a recent document revealing the new court date states that the new court date is going to be January 11,2021.
